SENNEBOGEN 895 E Hybrid port material handler with customized skip pan attachment 🚢

This configuration is a world’s first on a SENNEBOGEN material handler, resulting in most impressive loading cycles: Trucks can dump their load into the skip pan, and the SENNEBOGEN 895 loads it into the ship. ⏱️
At Gateway Terminal in Connecticut 🇺🇸, the world's largest material handler now showcases a massive advantage over the site’s conventional wire rope port crane: The SENNEBOGEN 895's skip pan attachment can rotate, whereas the crane cannot.
